{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_03_02",
  "title": "兵藤雫",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（雫の想いは伝わって）\n（二人の期間限定ユニットが始動した）",
      "startTime": 2.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 6.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんと二人で来るなんてびっくりしたよ\nしっかり想いを伝えたんだな",
      "startTime": 10.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "うん……瑠依さんと一緒に歌えるなんて夢みたい……\n緊張するけど……それ以上に、凄く嬉しい……！",
      "startTime": 19.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "それに優ちゃんとすみれちゃんも後押ししてくれた……\nトリエルは本当にいいグループ……",
      "startTime": 30.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ……\n私と組んで失敗だったなんて思われたくない……",
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな\n雫と天動さんの新ユニット、必ず成功させよう",
      "startTime": 42.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "今日の夕方から……瑠依さんとレッスン開始……\nうまくいくように……全力で頑張る……！",
      "startTime": 51.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "雫は新しいユニットを\nどんな風にしたいと考えてるんだ？",
      "startTime": 57.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "まだ考え中だけど……瑠依さんの相手にふさわしい……\nクールな兵藤雫を表現したい……",
      "startTime": 65.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "それから……私なりのやり方で……\n瑠依さんの魅力を引き出したい……",
      "startTime": 72.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "歴戦のアイドルオタクだからこそ\n天動さんの隠れた魅力を引き出せるってことか",
      "startTime": 78.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "ドルオタの名に懸けて……\n私が瑠依さんを輝かせてみせる……！",
      "startTime": 83.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "輝くのは天動さんだけじゃないぞ\n雫も負けないくらい輝いてもらわないと",
      "startTime": 90.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "うん……\n今はまだ、どうすればいいか分からないけど……",
      "startTime": 95.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたら瑠依さんと化学反応を起こせるのか……\n一緒に練習しながら……見つけていきたい……",
      "startTime": 105.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "頼もしいな。二人がどんなパフォーマンスを\n見せてくれるのか今から楽しみだ",
      "startTime": 112.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――雫と瑠依の限定ユニットがスタートして、数日後",
      "startTime": 116.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 118.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あれから天動さんと毎日練習してるんだろ？\n調子はどうなんだ？",
      "startTime": 122.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "ずーん……",
      "startTime": 124.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "分かりやすく落ち込んでるな……\n練習中にミスでもしたのか？",
      "startTime": 129.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "ミス以前の問題……\n瑠依さんは歌もダンスもハイレベルで……",
      "startTime": 134.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "曲の理解も凄く早い……もはや天才の領域……\n振り付けもあっという間に自分のものにして……",
      "startTime": 146.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "このままじゃ、下手な私とバランスが取れない……\n早く瑠依さんのレベルに追いつかないと……",
      "startTime": 155.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "レベルの差か……なんだか雫らしくないな",
      "startTime": 159.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "私らしくない？　どこが？",
      "startTime": 164.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "どこと言われると説明が難しいが……\nサニピではもっと和気あいあいとしてるだろ？",
      "startTime": 172.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "今回は瑠依さんが相手……\nだから、私が瑠依さんのやり方に合わせるべき……",
      "startTime": 179.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "私は実力も足りてないし、想いもうまく伝えられない\nもっと努力しないと……",
      "startTime": 192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（天動さんと組むことになって気負っているみたいだな）\n（肩に力が入り過ぎないといいが……）",
      "startTime": 198.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 202.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "今日も練習についていけなかった……\nそれに私の言葉が足りなくて……気まずい感じに……",
      "startTime": 208.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンはまだ始まったばかりだ\nそんなに焦らなくてもいいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 217.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "私も最初はそう思ってた……でも……\nそんな甘い考えじゃ……瑠依さんには追いつけない……",
      "startTime": 225.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "私は今まで……何度も困難を乗り越えてきた……\nだから今回も出来ると思ったけど……間違いだった……",
      "startTime": 235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "今までは、みんなが私の声に耳を傾けてくれた……\nサニピのみんなが私を理解しようとしてくれた……",
      "startTime": 249.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk021.m4a",
      "text": "サニピだから私は自分の気持ちを言葉に出来た……\n私はずっと、みんなの優しさに甘えてた……",
      "startTime": 261.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk022.m4a",
      "text": "私……勘違いしていた……\n私は一人じゃ何も出来ない……",
      "startTime": 272.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk023.m4a",
      "text": "サニピでは……さくらちゃんが引っ張ってくれて……\n怜ちゃんが前に出てくれて……",
      "startTime": 280.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk024.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんが支えてくれて……\n千紗ちゃんと励まし合って……",
      "startTime": 286.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk025.m4a",
      "text": "一人で乗り越えられたことなんて、一度もなかったのに\n一人でも出来るって勘違いしてた……",
      "startTime": 295.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "雫は遠慮しているようだが、みんなを頼りにしたように\nもっと天動さんを頼ってもいいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 304.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "今後二人の距離は縮まっていくはずだ\nそうして支え合えるようになっていけばいいんだ",
      "startTime": 310.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-szk026.m4a",
      "text": "でも……瑠依さんは私がお願いして組んでもらった……\nその私が迷惑を掛ける訳にはいかない……",
      "startTime": 319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "……なぁ、雫？\n雫にとって天動さんはどういう存在なんだ？",
      "startTime": 326.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
